Temporary workspace:
  install downloads and extracts files under TMPDIR when set, otherwise /var/tmp.
  Use TMPDIR=/path/on/a/larger/filesystem when /tmp is small.

Verify:
  systemctl status vault
  ${VAULT_MANAGER_CMD} status
EOF
}

